---
import LayoutDefault from "../layouts/layoutdefault.astro";

import Button from "../blocks/button.astro";

import Book from "../assets/images/book.svg";
import Snow from "../assets/images/snow.svg";
import Arrow from "../assets/images/arrow.svg";
import Arch from "../assets/images/arch.svg";
import Wave from "../assets/images/wave.svg";
import Circle from "../assets/images/circle.svg";
import Splash from "../assets/images/splash.svg";
import Pointer from "../assets/images/pointer.svg";
import Star from "../assets/images/star.svg";

const title = "Home";
const description = "My Description";
---

<LayoutDefault title={title} description={description}>
	<section class="dark">
		<div class="wrapper banner-intro">
			<div class="grid g-gap">
				<h1 class="fs-6 uppercase trim">
					We make<br /> your brand<br />
					<span style="color:var(--c-pink)">impossible</span> to ignore
				</h1>
				<p class="fs-3">We run your content, website, and ads, so you can run your business.</p>
				<div class="flex">
					<Button
						text="Book FREE Strategy Call"
						class="blue round arrow"
						href="https://connect.inkfish.co.za/hello/"
						target="_self"
					/>
					<Button
						text="Get FREE Brand Audit"
						class="yellow round arrow outline"
						href="https://connect.inkfish.co.za/audit/"
						target="_self"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="grid-icons">
				<div>
					<Book class="animate" stroke="var(--c-pink)" width={64} height={64} />
				</div>
				<div>
					<Wave class="animate" stroke="var(--c-orange)" width={64} height={64} />
					<Splash class="animate" fill="var(--c-blue)" width={64} height={64} />
				</div>
				<div>
					<Arrow class="animate" stroke="var(--c-green)" width={64} height={64} />
					<Circle class="animate" stroke="var(--c-red)" width={64} height={64} />
					<Snow class="animate" stroke="var(--c-yellow)" width={64} height={64} />
				</div>
				<div>
					<Arch class="animate" stroke="var(--c-yellow)" width={64} height={64} />
					<Pointer class="animate" stroke="var(--c-orange)" width={64} height={64} />
					<Star class="animate" fill="var(--c-blue)" width={64} height={64} />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tilt edge move gb center uppercase fs-3 bold balance">
			More time for you. More leads for your brand. <span style="color: var(--c-yellow);">Zero marketing meltdowns</span
			>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="dark">
		<div class="wrapper narrow grid g-gap g-center">
			<h2 class="balance fs-5 center">
				Inkfish is a South African <span style="color: var(--c-yellow);">digital marketing agency.</span>
			</h2>
			<p class="fs-4 center" style="line-height: 2;">
				We create scroll-stopping content, <span class="pill blue br-a">sleek websites</span>, <span
					class="pill pink br-e">smart ads</span
				>, and <span class="pill green br-r">brand strategies</span> for businesses who want to grow fast and look good doing
				it.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section>
		<div class="wrapper grid g-gap">
			<h2 class="balance fs-4 center" style="color: var(--c-green);">let's fix what's slowing you down</h2>
			<div class="grid-cards">
				<div class="card">
					<div>
						<Star class="bg orange animate" fill="var(--c-yellow)" width={64} height={64} />
						<Pointer class="bg blue animate" stroke="var(--c-yellow)" width={64} height={64} />
						<Arrow class="bg pink animate" stroke="var(--c-red)" width={64} height={64} />
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>
							<span class="pill c blue br-a fs-4">Before Inkfish</span>
						</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Your website's just… there. Not working.</li>
							<li>Your content gets ignored; or worse, it bores.</li>
							<li>Your ads are costing money without clear returns</li>
							<li>You're juggling too much and marketing's always last on the list</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<div>
						<Splash class="bg yellow animate" fill="var(--c-orange)" width={64} height={64} />
						<Snow class="bg green animate" stroke="var(--c-blue)" width={64} height={64} />
						<Circle class="bg red animate" stroke="var(--c-pink)" width={64} height={64} />
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>
							<span class="pill c blue br-a fs-4">After Inkfish</span>
						</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Your site works as hard as you do (and looks better doing it).</li>
							<li>Content? Click-worthy. Shareable. On-brand.</li>
							<li>Ads? ROI-driven, not guesswork.</li>
							<li>You? Back to what you do best, without dropping the marketing ball.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="wrapper">
			<p class="center fs-2">
				We're your full-stack marketing team-web, design, content, ads. Done right. Done for you.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="wrapper">
			<div class="dark tilt move yr center uppercase bold">
				<span> Inkfish plugs in like your in-house team, minus the overhead and hiring drama. </span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="dark">
		<div class="wrapper grid g-gap">
			<div class="services">
				<div class="intro">
					<div class="grid g-gap">
						<h2 class="balance fs-4" style="color: var(--c-green);">smart services. real results.</h2>
						<p>From brand building to clicks and conversions. We cover it all.</p>
						<p>Pick what you need or let us run the full system.</p>
						<Button href="services/" class="blue round arrow" text="View All Services" />
					</div>
					<div class="icons">
						<div>
							<Splash class="animate" fill="var(--c-orange)" width={64} height={64} />
						</div>
						<div>
							<Arrow class="animate" stroke="var(--c-pink)" width={64} height={64} />
							<Arch class="animate" stroke="var(--c-yellow)" width={64} height={64} />
						</div>
						<div>
							<Pointer class="animate" stroke="var(--c-red)" width={64} height={64} />
							<Star class="animate" fill="var(--c-green)" width={64} height={64} />
							<Wave class="animate" stroke="var(--c-blue)" width={64} height={64} />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="cards light">
					<ul role="list" class="stack">
						<li class="card grid g-gap">
							<h3 class="c yellow trim">branding</h3>
							<p>
								Looks that stop the scroll. Messaging that moves the needle. We design logos, brand guides, pitch decks,
								and stationery that build real recognition fast.
							</p>
							<div class="pill c yellow br-a">Starting From: R 4 500</div>
						</li>
						<li class="card grid g-gap">
							<h3 class="c pink trim">content & social</h3>
							<p>
								Posts that make people pause. Reels that get saved. We handle strategy, design, writing, SEO, and
								posting across Instagram, LinkedIn and Facebook. Need a blog too? We've got that.
							</p>
							<div class="pill c pink br-a">Starting From: R 7 000</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<ul role="list" class="stack">
						<li class="card grid g-gap">
							<h3 class="c orange trim">web design</h3>
							<p>
								A good-looking website is cute. A converting one is better. We design sites that load fast, sell hard,
								and scale with your brand. Maintenance, analytics, training and optimisations? Covered.
							</p>
							<div class="pill c orange br-a">Starting From: R 12 000</div>
						</li>
						<li class="card grid g-gap">
							<h3 class="c red trim">ads & funnels</h3>
							<p>
								Ads shouldn't feel like throwing money into the void. We build full-funnel campaigns on Meta and Google
								that connect spend to sales. Landing pages, email flows, and lead magnets? Done.
							</p>
							<div class="pill c red br-a">Starting From: R 2 900</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section style="background-color: var(--c-green);">
		<div class="wrapper grid g-gap">
			<h2 class="balance fs-4 center" style="color: var(--c-white);">what our clients say (and yes, we blushed)</h2>
			<div
				class="pill br-a bg white center bold c-text ct-green"
				style="padding: 0.5em 2em; border: unset; width: fit-content; margin-inline: auto"
			>
				Real results. No scripts. Just happy clients
			</div>
			<div class="reviews">
				<ul role="list">
					<li>
						"Inkfish has been our marketing team for more than six years. They jump in fast, finish the work, and save
						us the cost of minimum five hires. Their skill keeps opening new doors."
						<div class="person">Phillip Harmse - UXI</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish understands what we want and what we actually need. We left once, tried others, and came straight
						back. Their quality is unmatched."
						<div class="person">Madeleine Nel - Silver Edge</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish delivered a website I love, creative and fast. Every request met with a no-nonsense 'can-do'
						attitude. They waited for my feedback without pressure and still turned updates around in hours. The whole
						team made the process smooth and gave me confidence to keep growing my site."
						<div class="person">Gail Schoeman</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish's support was clear, timely, and fast. They fixed our booking-system hiccups straight after hosting
						handover, and reservations now run without a hitch."
						<div class="person">Windhoek Pet Lodge</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish's dynamic approach to marketing and design has been a game changer for my business. They have been
						ale to accommadate my needs on very short notice. I valie them as a trusted business partner and look
						forward to the future with Inkfish."
						<div class="person">Dylan Mattison</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"The partnership that we developed with Inkfish has been a turning point fo us as a Business Chamber. Our
						social media presence especially, took us to a new level. We have been receiving more views and interest
						than ever before. The designers and contact persons are always on the ready, and it is absolutely amazing
						how a small idea can take form and become exactly what we envisioned. The attention to detail is so evident
						in all aspects."
						<div class="person">Bernadette Schaap</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<ul role="list" aria-hidden="true">
					<li>
						"Inkfish has been our marketing team for more than six years. They jump in fast, finish the work, and save
						us the cost of minimum five hires. Their skill keeps opening new doors."
						<div class="person">Phillip Harmse - UXI</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish understands what we want and what we actually need. We left once, tried others, and came straight
						back. Their quality is unmatched."
						<div class="person">Madeleine Nel - Silver Edge</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish delivered a website I love, creative and fast. Every request met with a no-nonsense 'can-do'
						attitude. They waited for my feedback without pressure and still turned updates around in hours. The whole
						team made the process smooth and gave me confidence to keep growing my site."
						<div class="person">Gail Schoeman</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish's support was clear, timely, and fast. They fixed our booking-system hiccups straight after hosting
						handover, and reservations now run without a hitch."
						<div class="person">Windhoek Pet Lodge</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"Inkfish's dynamic approach to marketing and design has been a game changer for my business. They have been
						ale to accommadate my needs on very short notice. I valie them as a trusted business partner and look
						forward to the future with Inkfish."
						<div class="person">Dylan Mattison</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						"The partnership that we developed with Inkfish has been a turning point fo us as a Business Chamber. Our
						social media presence especially, took us to a new level. We have been receiving more views and interest
						than ever before. The designers and contact persons are always on the ready, and it is absolutely amazing
						how a small idea can take form and become exactly what we envisioned. The attention to detail is so evident
						in all aspects."
						<div class="person">Bernadette Schaap</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="dark">
		<div class="wrapper banner-intro" style="gap: 2em">
			<div class="grid g-gap g-start-x">
				<div style="display: flex; flex-flow: wrap; gap: 1em;">
					<span class="pill bg red br-a">no jargon</span>
					<span class="pill bg pink br-e" style="color: var(--c-black)">No pressure</span>
					<span class="pill white br-a">just results</span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="fs-4">
					Let's build your marketing System <span class="c yellow">(and make it actually work)</span>
				</h2>
				<p>Book a free strategy call or brand audit. We'll show you where the gaps are and exactly how to fix them.</p>
				<Button
					text="Book a FREE Strategy Call"
					class="blue round arrow"
					href="https://connect.inkfish.co.za/hello/"
					target="_self"
				/>
			</div>
			<div>
				<img src="./images/handshake.avif" alt="handshake" width="500" height="401" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</LayoutDefault>
